Don't know about Gull Rock, but Red Lake does and it's in the same chain of lakes.
Don't know about Gull Rock, but Red Lake does and it's in the same chain of lakes.

I am not fortunate to go in May, but have spoken to many that have and it is outstanding. there are some lakers taken out of Gullrock in the spring, I believe in or near the Chukuni river coming out of Red Lake.
